com.acrolinx.javasdk.gui

Enum Images

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Images>
      • com.acrolinx.javasdk.gui.Images
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Images>

    public enum Images
extends Enum<Images>
    The enum Images provides image names and default file names for image files. Note: Do not use null but use NULL instead.
